<h2>Display with orderBy Filter</h2>

To sort the table, add an orderBy filter:<br><br>
<b>x in names | orderBy : 'Country'</b><br><br>

<pre>
  &lt;table&gt;
  &lt;tr ng-repeat="x in names | orderBy : 'Country'"&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;{{ x.Name }}&lt;/td&gt;
    &lt;td&gt;{{ x.Country }}&lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
</pre>

